name: Lavender Key Rings
description:
I have taken some of my more popular designs and made these pretty appliqued key-rings. Just give them a squeeze to release the aroma. Would make a great partner to a matching purse or pencil case.

I have used cotton and linen carefully appliqued each design, stuffing them with lavender and hand sewing up the bottom. They are attached to the metal key ring with some thick cotton string.

Lavender has come from a farm in the cotswolds. 

Size approx 5cm x 7cm 

Fabrics used my vary from those shown.

name: Cake Coin Purses
description:
What's your favourite? Strawberry cheesecake or chocolate cake. A cute and fun little purse great for coins, keys, or a bit of make-up.

Using cotton fabrics I have carefully appliqued  different cake designs. This purse has a nylon zip and is fully lined.

Designed and handmade by me in my little house in the New forest 

Approx 9cm x 14cm

Fabrics used for the applique may vary in pattern from that shown.

name: *NEW* Balloon Lavender Keyrings
description:
Cute balloon key-rings in a rainbow of colours and filled with lavender. Just give them a squeeze to release the aroma. A great partner to my balloon coin purses.

Using cotton fabrics I have appliqued and machine embroidered balloons in five different colours, they are stuffed with lavender and then attached to a split ring with strong cotton string.

Lavender has come from a farm in the cotswolds. 

Size approx 5cm x 7cm

name: *NEW* Rainbow of Balloons Cushion
description:
A rainbow of balloons foating in the sky, how high will they go ? A colourful and fun cushion for a childs room.

Using cotton fabrics balloons and clouds have been carefully appliqued on to blue sky print fabric. Backed in red striped cotton and fastening with a button this cushion it is filled with a polyester cushion pad.

Handmade and an original design from DinkyDaisy.
 
Size 33cm x 33cm.

This is not a toy and has small parts which are unsuitable for small children.

name: *NEW* Balloon Coin Purse
description:
Up up and away a cute and fun balloon coin purse, an essential for keeping cards and coins tidy and safe. Partner with a lavender key ring for a great gift.

Blue spotty balloon and a white cloud have been appliqued and machine embroidered on to red striped cotton. This purse is fully lined with blue skies fabric and fastens with a white zip.

Handmade and an original design from DinkyDaisy.

Size 9cm x 14 cm approx.
